    zubereitung: ["Preheat the oven to 150C/300F/Gas 2.", "Toss the beef and flour together in a bowl with some salt and black pepper.", "Heat a large casserole until hot, add half of the rapeseed oil and enough of the beef to just cover the bottom of the casserole.", "Fry until browned on each side, then remove and set aside. Repeat with the remaining oil and beef.", "Return the beef to the pan, add the wine and cook until the volume of liquid has reduced by half, then add the stock, onion, carrots, thyme and mustard, and season well with salt and pepper.", "Cover with a lid and place in the oven for two hours.", "Remove from the oven, check the seasoning and set aside to cool. Remove the thyme.", "When the beef is cool and you're ready to assemble the pie, preheat the oven to 200C/400F/Gas 6."],
