    zutaten: ["225g Kartoffeln", "1 kleine Fennel", "1 clove finely chopped Knoblauch", "75 ml Milch", "100ml Sahne", "For Greasing Butter", "to serve Parmesan"],
    zubereitung: ["Heat oven to 180C/160C fan/gas 4. Put potatoes, fennel, and garlic in a medium non-stick pan. Pour in milk and double cream, season well and simmer gently, covered, for 10 mins, stirring halfway through, until potatoes are just tender.", "Divide the mixture between 2 small (about 150ml) buttered ramekins and scatter with Parmesan. Bake for 40 mins until the potatoes are golden and tender when pierced with a knife. Snip the reserved fennel fronds over before serving."],
