    zubereitung: ["In a large bowl, whisk together 1/2 cup buckwheat flour, 2/3 cup all-purpose flour, 1/2 teaspoon salt, and 1 teaspoon yeast.", "Make a well in the center and pour in 1 cup warm milk, whisking until the batter is smooth.", "Cover the bowl and let the batter rise until doubled, about 1 hour.", "Enrich and Rest the Batter\r\nStir 2 tablespoons melted butter and 1 egg yolk into the batter.", "In a separate bowl, whisk 1 egg white until stiff, but not dry.", "Fold the whisked egg white into the batter.", "Cover the bowl and let the batter stand 20 minutes.", "Pan-Fry the Blini\r\nHeat butter in a large nonstick skillet over medium heat."],
