    zubereitung: ["1\r\nIn a dutch oven or slow cooker, add all the spices, beef broth and lemon juice. Stir to combine..", "2\r\nAdd the beef and turn to coat, spoon some sauce over the top.", "3\r\nCover and cook on low for 8-10 hours.", "4\r\nAfter cooking, remove beef and use two forks to shred. Discard any excess fat.", "5\r\nSkim fat off of the top of the liquid remaining.", "6\r\nMix shredded beef into sauce. Keep warm until you are ready to serve.", "7\r\nBuild wrap by spreading garlic sauce on the pita. Top with beef and add garnishes to your liking.", "8\r\nFold it burrito style."],
